<div class="container" style="margin-top: 120px; margin-bottom: 60px; max-width: 800px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #1e1b4b; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">Ch&#237;nh S&#225;ch B&#7843;o M&#7853;t</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Cam k&#7871;t b&#7843;o v&#7879; tuy&#7879;t &#273;&#7889;i d&#7919; li&#7879;u v&#224; quy&#7873;n ri&#234;ng t&#432; c&#225; nh&#226;n c&#7911;a b&#7841;n t&#7841;i TourBuddy.</p>

    <div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); padding: 30px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">1. Thu th&#7853;p d&#7919; li&#7879;u th&#244;ng tin</h2>
        <p>Ch&#250;ng t&#244;i ch&#7881; thu th&#7853;p c&#225;c th&#244;ng tin c&#225; nh&#226;n c&#7847;n thi&#7871;t ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho vi&#7879;c v&#7853;n h&#224;nh tour du l&#7883;ch, bao g&#7891;m: H&#7885; t&#234;n, Email, S&#7889; &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i, &#272;&#7883;a ch&#7881; v&#224; Th&#244;ng tin thanh to&#225;n an to&#224;n.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5rem;">2. S&#7917; d&#7909;ng th&#244;ng tin thu th&#7853;p</h2>
        <p>Th&#244;ng tin c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng &#273;&#7875;: X&#225;c nh&#7853;n &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7863;t tour, x&#7917; l&#253; giao d&#7883;ch thanh to&#225;n tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n, g&#7917;i email x&#225;c nh&#7853;n &#273;&#7863;t ch&#7895; v&#224; g&#7917;i th&#244;ng b&#225;o khi c&#243; thay &#273;&#7893;i quan tr&#7885;ng v&#7873; l&#7883;ch kh&#7903;i h&#224;nh.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5rem;">3. Cam k&#7871;t b&#7843;o m&#7853;t an to&#224;n</h2>
        <p>TourBuddy &#225;p d&#7909;ng c&#225;c bi&#7879;n ph&#225;p m&#227; h&#243;a k&#7929; thu&#7853;t s&#7889; ti&#234;n ti&#7871;n nh&#7845;t (giao th&#7913;c b&#7843;o m&#7853;t SSL/TLS) &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o d&#7919; li&#7879;u c&#7911;a b&#7841;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c truy&#7873;n &#273;i an to&#224;n v&#224; b&#7843;o m&#7853;t ho&#224;n to&#224;n kh&#7887;i c&#225;c h&#224;nh vi truy c&#7853;p tr&#225;i ph&#233;p t&#7915; b&#234;n ngo&#224;i.</p>
